OL,6,FThis can include not just food and
OL,7,Fdrink, but also the cost of calls,
OL,8,Faccommodation and transport to a hotel
OL,9,For home. The CAA adds that "luxury
OL,10,Fhotels and alcohol" are unlikely to be
OL,11,Fcovered.
